#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:38
msgid ""
"or access the transaction list by clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon on the :guilabel:`Bank` journal and "
"selecting :guilabel:`Transactions`, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and select :guilabel:`Import records`."
