msgstr ":doc:`batch_sdd`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:3
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) customer payments"
msgstr "Paiements clients par prélèvement SEPA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:7
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries. With **SEPA Direct Debit** "
"(SDD), customers sign a mandate that authorizes you to collect future "
"payments from their bank accounts. This is particularly useful for recurring "
"payments based on a :doc:`subscription </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"Le SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) est une initiative d'intégration des "
"paiements de l'Union européenne qui facilite les paiements électroniques "
"standardisés et simplifiés en euros dans les pays participants. Avec le "
"**prélèvement SEPA** (SDD), les clients signent un mandat qui vous autorise "
"à collecter les paiements futurs depuis leurs comptes bancaires. Cela est "
"particulièrement utile pour les paiements récurrents basés sur un "
":doc:`abonnement </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:13
msgid ""
"You can record customer |sdd| mandates in Odoo and generate XML files "
"listing payments to be collected with the mandates. :ref:`Uploading these "
"files to your bank <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` instructs them to collect "
"these payments from your customers."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez enregistrer les mandats de prélèvement |sdd| des clients dans "
"Odoo et générer des fichiers XML listant les paiements à collecter avec les "
"mandats. :ref:`Télécharger ces fichiers sur votre banque <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>` lui donne instruction de collecter ces paiements auprès de "
"vos clients."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:18
msgid ""
"|sdd| is supported by all SEPA countries, which includes the 27 member "
"states of the European Union as well as additional countries."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| est pris en charge par tous les pays SEPA, ce qui inclut les 27 États "
"membres de l'Union européenne ainsi que des pays supplémentaires."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:20
msgid ""
"`List of all SEPA countries <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Liste de tous les pays SEPA <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/"
"document-library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:29
msgid "Creditor identifier"
msgstr "Identifiant créancier"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:31
msgid ""
"To enable |sdd| for customer payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Then, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section again, set the company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer |sdd| pour les paiements clients, aller à "
":menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, faire "
"défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Paiements clients`, activer "
":guilabel:`Prélèvement SEPA (SDD)`, et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`. "
"Ensuite, faire défiler à nouveau jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Paiements "
"clients`, définir l':guilabel:`Identifiant créancier` de l'entreprise, et "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:37
msgid ""
"The creditor identifier is provided by your bank or the authority "
"responsible for delivering them in your country. For testing purposes, you "
"can use the test creditor identifier `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."
msgstr ""
"L'identifiant créancier est fourni par votre banque ou l'autorité "
"responsable de les délivrer dans votre pays. À des fins de test, vous pouvez "
"utiliser l'identifiant créancier de test `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:42
msgid "PAIN file version"
msgstr "Version du fichier PAIN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:44
msgid ""
"By default, the :ref:`SEPA-compliant XML files <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` "
"generated by Odoo use the |sdd| **PAIN.008.001.02** format. If your bank "
"requires the updated 2023 version, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`. Then, in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, "
"set the :guilabel:`SEPA Pain version` field to :guilabel:`Updated 2023 (Pain "
"008.001.08)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:53
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit Mandates"
msgstr "Mandats de prélèvement SEPA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:55
msgid ""
"An |sdd| mandate is a legal document authorizing a company to debit funds "
"from a customer's bank account. It includes key information, such as the "
"customer's name and IBAN, the mandate's start and end date, and the "
"mandate's unique identifier. The mandate form must be filled in and signed "
"by the customer."
msgstr ""
"Un |sdd| mandat est un document juridique autorisant une entreprise à "
"débiter des fonds du compte bancaire d'un client. Il comprend des "
"informations clés, telles que le nom et l'IBAN du client, les dates de début "
"et de fin du mandat, et l'identifiant unique du mandat. Le formulaire de "
"mandat doit être rempli et signé par le client."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:61
msgid "Creating mandates"
msgstr "Créer des mandats"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:63
msgid "To create an |sdd| mandate:"
msgstr "Pour créer un |sdd| mandat :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:65
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Direct Debit Mandates`."
msgstr ""
"Aller dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Clients --> Mandats de "
"prélèvement`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:66
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` and fill out the fields."
msgstr "Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau` et remplir les champs."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:67
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Print` to generate a PDF of the mandate form, then send it "
"to the customer for signature."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:69
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Validate` to activate the mandate."
msgstr "Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Valider` pour activer le mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:72
msgid ""
"A valid IBAN must be defined in the :guilabel:`Account Number` field of "
"the :doc:`bank journal <../bank>` used to receive |sdd| payments for the "
"mandate."
msgstr ""
"Un IBAN valide doit être défini dans le champ :guilabel:`Numéro de compte` "
"du :doc:`journal bancaire <../bank>` utilisé pour recevoir les |sdd| "
"paiements pour le mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:76
msgid ""
"To print the mandate form after the mandate has been validated, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then select :guilabel:`Mandate "
"form`."
msgstr ""
"Pour imprimer le formulaire de mandat après validation du mandat, cliquer "
"sur l'icône :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`engrenage`), puis sélectionner "
":guilabel:`Formulaire de mandat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:78
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SDD Scheme` depends on the type of customer: "
"Select :guilabel:`CORE` for B2C customers and :guilabel:`B2B` for B2B "
