#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:66
msgid "Next, click the :guilabel:`Approve Report` button."
msgstr "Ensuite, cliquez sur le bouton :guilabel:`Approuver le rapport`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:None
