"Ce  `certificat <https://www.odoo.com/my/contract/french-certification/>`_ "
"est délivré par Odoo SA aux utilisateurs d’Odoo Enterprise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:641
msgid "To get the certification, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour obtenir la certification, suivez les étapes suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:643
msgid ""
":doc:`Install </applications/general/apps_modules>` the :guilabel:`France - "
"VAT Anti-Fraud Certification for Point of Sale (CGI 286 I-3 bis)` "
