":doc:`Installez </applications/general/apps_modules>` le "
"module :guilabel:`France - Certification anti-fraude TVA pour point de vente "
"(CGI 286 I-3 bis)` (`l10n_fr_pos_cert`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:645
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Country` field on the :doc:`company record </applications/"
"general/companies>` to encrypt entries for the inalterability check."
msgstr ""
"Renseignez le champ :guilabel:`Pays` dans la :doc:`fiche société </"
