#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:72
msgid ""
"The :doc:`VAT summary <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` provides a "
"detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, and exempt transactions. Like "
"other :doc:`financial reports <../accounting/reporting>`, the VAT summary "
"can be filtered by period, compared against other periods, and exported in "
"Excel and PDF formats, ensuring compliance with Jordanian tax laws."
msgstr ""
"Le :doc:`résumé de TVA <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` fournit une "
"ventilation détaillée des transactions taxables, à taux zéro et exonérées. "
"Comme les autres :doc:`rapports financiers <../accounting/reporting>`, le "
"résumé de TVA peut être filtré par période, comparé à d'autres périodes et "
"exporté aux formats Excel et PDF, garantissant la conformité avec les lois "
"fiscales jordaniennes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:80
msgid "E-invoicing with JoFotara"
msgstr "Facturation électronique avec JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:82
msgid ""
"E-invoicing with JoFotara is integrated with Odoo, ensuring compliance with "
"Jordanian government's technical and legal requirements for electronic "
"invoicing. The JoFotara integration in Odoo directly connects with the "
"Jordanian e-invoicing platform, allowing companies to:"
msgstr ""
"La facturation électronique avec JoFotara est intégrée à Odoo, garantissant "
"la conformité avec les exigences techniques et légales du gouvernement "
"jordanien en matière de facturation électronique. L'intégration JoFotara "
"dans Odoo se connecte directement à la plateforme jordanienne de facturation "
"électronique, permettant aux entreprises de :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:86
msgid "generate compliant electronic invoices"
msgstr "générer des factures électroniques conformes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:87
msgid "submit invoices in real time for validation"
msgstr "soumettre les factures en temps réel pour validation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:88
msgid "track invoice statuses directly within Odoo"
msgstr "suivre les statuts des factures directement dans Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:90
msgid ""
"The integration requires first creating an account with JoFotara, then "
"generating API credentials, and finally entering those credentials in your "
"Odoo database to link the two."
msgstr ""
"L'intégration nécessite d'abord de créer un compte avec JoFotara, puis de "
"générer des identifiants API et enfin de saisir ces identifiants dans votre "
"base de données Odoo pour lier les deux."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:95
msgid ""
"`Government manuals <manuals_>`_ provide instructions for creating an "
"account and generating the API credentials."
msgstr ""
"Les `manuels gouvernementaux <manuals_>`_ fournissent des instructions pour "
"créer un compte et générer les identifiants API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:106
msgid "Link Odoo to JoFotara"
msgstr "Lier Odoo à JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:108
msgid ""
"If you don't already have an account, create one by going to the `government "
"manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps in the **Procedure Manual "
"for Joining the Jordanian National Electronic Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Si vous n'avez pas encore de compte, créez-en un en accédant à la page des "
"`manuels gouvernementaux <manuals_>`_ et en suivant les étapes du **Manuel "
"de procédure pour rejoindre le système national jordanien de facturation "
"électronique**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:111
msgid ""
"Generate API credentials (Activity Number, Secret Key, and Client ID) by "
"going to the `government manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps "
"in **Procedure Manual for Linking to the Jordanian National Electronic "
"Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Générer les identifiants API (Numéro d'activité, Clé secrète et ID client) "
"en accédant à la page des `manuels gouvernementaux <manuals_>`_ et en "
"suivant les étapes du **Manuel de procédure pour se connecter au système "
"national jordanien de facturation électronique**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:114
msgid ""
"In your Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` section, enter "
"the API credentials generated previously:"
msgstr ""
"Dans votre base de données Odoo, allez dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres`. Dans la section :guilabel:`Facturation "
"électronique (Jordanie)`, saisissez les identifiants API générés "
"précédemment :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:118
msgid ":guilabel:`Activity Number` (income source sequence)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Numéro d'activité` (séquence de source de revenus)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:119
msgid ":guilabel:`JoFotara Secret Key`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Clé secrète JoFotara`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:120
msgid ":guilabel:`JoFotara Client ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID client JoFotara`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:122
msgid "Enter the :guilabel:`Taxpayer type`:"
msgstr "Saisissez le :guilabel:`Type de contribuable` :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unregistered in the sales tax`: for businesses not registered for "
"sales tax. No tax on the invoice line is required."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Non enregistré pour la taxe de vente` : pour les entreprises non "
"enregistrées pour la taxe de vente. Aucune taxe sur la ligne de facture "
"n'est requise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Registered in the sales tax`: for businesses registered under the "
"standard sales tax system. One tax computed as a percentage is required per "
"invoice line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Enregistré pour la taxe de vente` : pour les entreprises "
"enregistrées sous le régime standard de taxe de vente. Une taxe calculée en "
"pourcentage est requise par ligne de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Registered in the special sales tax`: for businesses subject to "
"special sales tax regulations. One tax computed as a percentage and one "
"fixed tax per invoice line are required per invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Enregistré pour la taxe de vente spéciale` : pour les entreprises "
"soumises à des réglementations spéciales de taxe de vente. Une taxe calculée "
"en pourcentage et une taxe fixe par ligne de facture sont requises par "
"facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:132
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/vietnam.rst:130
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Cliquez sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:135
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` section is missing from "
"the :guilabel:`Settings`, make sure the :guilabel:`Jordan E-Invoicing` "
"module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Si la section :guilabel:`Facturation électronique (Jordanie)` est absente "
"des :guilabel:`Paramètres`, vérifier que le module :guilabel:`Facturation "
"électronique jordanienne` est :ref:`installé <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:142
msgid "Company and customers"
msgstr "Entreprise et clients"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:144
msgid ""
"The JoFotara invoicing workflow requires address information related to the "
"company that sends the invoices and the customers who receive them:"
msgstr ""
"Le flux de facturation JoFotara nécessite des informations d'adresse "
"relatives à l'entreprise qui envoie les factures et aux clients qui les "
"reçoivent :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:147
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Utilisateurs & Sociétés --> Sociétés` "
"et sélectionner l'entreprise qui utilisera JoFotara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:149
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Company Name`, :guilabel:`Tax ID` (TIN), "
"and :guilabel:`Country`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"Remplir le :guilabel:`Nom de la société`, le :guilabel:`N° de TVA` (NIF) et "
"le :guilabel:`Pays`. Si souhaité, remplir des champs facultatifs "
"supplémentaires tels que :guilabel:`Rue`, :guilabel:`Ville`, "
":guilabel:`État` et :guilabel:`Code postal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:154
msgid "The :guilabel:`Country` must be set to :guilabel:`Jordan`."
msgstr "Le :guilabel:`Pays` doit être défini sur :guilabel:`Jordanie`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:155
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company Name` must match the name that is registered with the "
"Income and Sales Tax Department (ISTD)."
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`Nom de la société` doit correspondre au nom enregistré auprès "
"du Département de l'impôt sur le revenu et de la taxe de vente (ISTD)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:157
msgid "The company's :guilabel:`Currency` must be set to :guilabel:`JOD`."
msgstr ""
"La :guilabel:`Devise` de l'entreprise doit être définie sur :guilabel:`JOD`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:160
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`."
msgstr "Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Clients --> Clients`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:161
msgid ""
"For each customer whose invoices will be sent to JoFotara, click on the "
"customer to open the form view, and complete the :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`Tax ID`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"Pour chaque client dont les factures seront envoyées à JoFotara, cliquer sur "
"le client pour ouvrir le formulaire et compléter le :guilabel:`Pays` et le "
":guilabel:`N° de TVA`. Si souhaité, remplir des champs facultatifs "
"supplémentaires tels que :guilabel:`Rue`, :guilabel:`Ville`, "
":guilabel:`État` et :guilabel:`Code postal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:169
msgid "Sending invoices to JoFotara via Odoo"
msgstr "Envoyer des factures à JoFotara via Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:171
msgid ""
"Once the company has been :ref:`linked with JoFotara <localizations/jordan/"
"linking-jofotara>` and the :ref:`company and customers have been properly "
"configured <localizations/jordan/company-and-contacts>`, invoices can be "
"sent to JoFotara via Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Une fois l'entreprise :ref:`liée à JoFotara <localizations/jordan/linking-"
"jofotara>` et :ref:`l'entreprise et les clients correctement configurés "
"<localizations/jordan/company-and-contacts>`, les factures peuvent être "
"envoyées à JoFotara via Odoo :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:175
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices` and open a "
"confirmed (posted) invoice."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Clients --> Factures` et ouvrir une "
"facture confirmée (comptabilisée)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:178
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send` window, select :guilabel:`Send JoFotara e-invoice` "
"and click :guilabel:`Send & Print`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:181
msgid "When an invoice is sent to JoFotara, Odoo does the following:"
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une facture est envoyée à JoFotara, Odoo effectue les actions "
"suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:183
msgid "generates the invoice in the required format (UBL 1.2)"
msgstr "génère la facture dans le format requis (UBL 1.2)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:184
msgid "submits the invoice to JoFotara for validation"
msgstr "soumet la facture à JoFotara pour validation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:185
msgid "receives the QR code from JoFotara on the invoice's PDF"
msgstr "reçoit le QR code de JoFotara sur le PDF de la facture"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:188
msgid ""
"Multiple invoices can be :ref:`sent at once <accounting/invoice/sending>` to "
"JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Plusieurs factures peuvent être :ref:`envoyées simultanément <accounting/"
"invoice/sending>` à JoFotara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:189
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, filter the invoices by "
"their :ref:`localizations/jordan/jofotara-state` to see the invoices that "
"have either been sent or not been sent to JoFotara."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la vue liste des :guilabel:`Factures`, filtrer les factures par leur "
":ref:`localizations/jordan/jofotara-state` pour voir les factures qui ont "
"été envoyées ou non à JoFotara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:192
msgid ""
"In the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`adjust settings`) menu, add "
"the :guilabel:`JoFotara State` and :guilabel:`JoFotara Error` fields to see "
"the sending state and any errors in the list view, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Dans le menu :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`ajuster les paramètres`)"
", ajouter les champs :guilabel:`État JoFotara` et :guilabel:`Erreur "
"JoFotara` pour voir respectivement l'état d'envoi et les éventuelles erreurs "
"dans la vue liste."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:197
msgid ""
"There is an inherent difference in how values are approximated in Odoo and "
"ISTD due to the differing system architectures. JOD values in Odoo are "
"stored and approximated to three decimals, whereas ISTD expects values to "
"have nine decimals. As a result, an insignificant difference is inevitable "
"and arises between the values stores in Odoo and the values reported to "
"ISTD, which can have an error margin of <0.01."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:206
msgid "JoFotara State"
msgstr "État JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:208
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`JoFotara State` field in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab of "
"confirmed invoices reflects the current state of the document in JoFotara. "
"It can be changed manually to reflect the actual state of the invoices in "
"cases where a technical error or timeout prevents Odoo from updating it "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Le champ :guilabel:`État JoFotara` dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Autres infos` "
"des factures confirmées reflète l'état actuel du document dans JoFotara. Il "
"peut être modifié manuellement pour refléter l'état réel des factures dans "
"les cas où une erreur technique ou un délai d'expiration empêche Odoo de le "
"mettre à jour automatiquement."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:216
msgid "Validating QR codes (Sanad app)"
msgstr "Valider les QR codes (application Sanad)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:218
msgid ""
"To validate the QR code received from JoFotara on the invoice, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
