"Go to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and "
"select the bank account for which you want to activate PayNow. Set "
"the :guilabel:`Proxy Type` and fill in the :guilabel:`Proxy Value` field "
"depending on the type you chose."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:25
msgid ""
"The account holder's country must be set to `Singapore` on its contact form."
msgstr ""
"Le pays du titulaire du compte doit être défini sur `Singapore` dans son "
"formulaire de contact."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, open the "
"bank journal, then fill out the :guilabel:`Account Number` "
"and :guilabel:`Bank` under the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Journaux`, ouvrir "
"le journal bancaire, puis remplir le :guilabel:`Numéro de compte` et la "
":guilabel:`Banque` sous l'onglet :guilabel:`Écritures comptables`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Bank Account's journal configuration"
msgstr "Configuration du journal du compte bancaire"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:46
msgid "Issue invoices with PayNow QR codes"
msgstr "Émettre des factures avec des codes QR PayNow"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:48
msgid ""
"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and set "
"the :guilabel:`Payment QR-code` option to *EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code*."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la création d'une nouvelle facture, ouvrir l'onglet "
":guilabel:`Autres informations` et définir l'option :guilabel:`Code QR de "
"paiement` sur *Code QR présenté par le commerçant EMV*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Select EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code option"
msgstr "Sélectionner l'option Code QR présenté par le commerçant EMV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:54
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is the one you configured, as "
"Odoo uses this field to generate the PayNow QR code."
msgstr ""
"S'assurer que la :guilabel:`Banque destinataire` est celle que vous avez "
"configurée, car Odoo utilise ce champ pour générer le code QR PayNow."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:3
msgid "Spain"
msgstr "Espagne"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:8
msgid ""
"Install the 🇪🇸 **Spanish** :doc:`fiscal localization package <../"
"fiscal_localizations>` to get all the default accounting features of the "
"Spanish localization."
msgstr ""
"Installer le package de :doc:`localisation fiscale <../fiscal_localizations>"
"` 🇪🇸 **espagnol** pour obtenir toutes les fonctionnalités comptables par "
"défaut de la localisation espagnole."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:11
msgid ""
"Three **Spanish** localizations exist, each with its own pre-configured "
"**PGCE** charts of accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Il existe trois localisations **espagnoles**, chacune avec son propre plan "
"comptable **PGCE** préconfiguré :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:13
msgid "Spain - SMEs (2008);"
msgstr "Espagne - PME (2008) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:14
msgid "Spain - Complete (2008);"
msgstr "Espagne - Complet (2008) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:15
msgid "Spain - Non-profit entities (2008)."
msgstr "Espagne - Entités à but non lucratif (2008)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:17
msgid ""
"To select the one to use, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings` and select a package in the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Pour sélectionner celle à utiliser, aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres` et sélectionner un package dans la section "
":guilabel:`Localisation fiscale`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:21
msgid ""
"You can only change the accounting package as long as you have not created "
"any accounting entry."
msgstr ""
"Il est possible de changer de package comptable uniquement tant qu'aucune "
"écriture comptable n'a été créée."

