#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:99
msgid "Veri*Factu"
msgstr "Veri*Factu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:102
msgid ""
"Producers of Veri*Factu billing systems must self-certify their compliance "
"with the regulations. :download:`Download Odoo's \"declaración "
"responsable\"<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"
msgstr ""
"Les producteurs de systèmes de facturation Veri*Factu doivent auto-certifier "
"leur conformité à la réglementation. :download:`Télécharger la \"declaración "
"responsable\" d'Odoo<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:105
msgid ""
"**Veri*Factu** is an e-Invoicing system used by the Spanish Tax Agency. It "
"is mandatory for most taxpayers in Spain, except for those who use the SII "
"system or are under a regional tax regime (i.e., TicketBai)."
msgstr ""
"**Veri*Factu** est un système de facturation électronique utilisé par "
"l'administration fiscale espagnole. Il est obligatoire pour la plupart des "
"contribuables en Espagne, à l'exception de ceux qui utilisent le système SII "
"ou sont soumis à un régime fiscal régional (c'est-à-dire TicketBai)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:109
msgid ""
"Odoo allows :ref:`invoices <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` and "
"Point of Sale :ref:`orders <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` to be "
"automatically sent to the tax authorities."
msgstr ""
"Odoo permet d'envoyer automatiquement les :ref:`factures <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>` et les :ref:`commandes <localizations/spain/veri-"
"factu-orders>` Point de Vente aux autorités fiscales."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:117
msgid "To enable **Veri\\*Factu**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour activer **Veri\\*Factu**, suivre les étapes suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:119
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app to make sure your company's :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`Tax ID` are correctly set in the :ref:`Companies <general/"
"companies/company>` section."
msgstr ""
"Ouvrir l'application Paramètres pour s'assurer que le :guilabel:`Pays` et le "
":guilabel:`Numéro de TVA` de votre société sont correctement définis dans la "
"section :ref:`Sociétés <general/companies/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:121
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu "
"(l10n_es_edi_verifactu)` module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installer <general/install>` le module :guilabel:`Espagne - Veri*Factu "
"(l10n_es_edi_verifactu)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:123
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section, check the :guilabel:`Enable "
"Veri*Factu` option, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"certificates` to add a certificate."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, "
"descendre jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu`, cocher l'option "
":guilabel:`Activer Veri*Factu`, puis cliquer sur :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Gérer les certificats` pour ajouter un certificat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:126
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la vue liste :guilabel:`Certificats pour Veri\\*Factu`, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:127
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select a certificate file and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Password` needed to open the certificate (if there is one)."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Téléverser votre fichier`, puis sélectionner un "
"fichier de certificat et saisir le :guilabel:`Mot de passe` nécessaire pour "
"ouvrir le certificat (s'il y en a un)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:131
msgid "At least one certificate has to be uploaded."
msgstr "Au moins un certificat doit être téléversé."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:132
msgid ""
"By default Veri*Factu is in testing mode. The data is sent to test servers "
"and is not considered official. When official data can be sent to the "
"production servers, go to the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section in "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` and disable :guilabel:`Test Environment`."
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, Veri*Factu est en mode test. Les données sont envoyées aux "
"serveurs de test et ne sont pas considérées comme officielles. Lorsque les "
"données officielles peuvent être envoyées aux serveurs de production, aller "
"dans la section :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` des :guilabel:`Paramètres` et "
"désactiver :guilabel:`Environnement de test`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:142
msgid ""
"Once an :doc:`invoice <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` is "
"confirmed, it can be :ref:`sent <accounting/invoice/sending>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` window, the Veri*Factu option is available if "
"Veri*Factu has been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Une fois qu'une :doc:`facture <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"est confirmée, elle peut être :ref:`envoyée <accounting/invoice/sending>`. "
"Dans la fenêtre :guilabel:`Envoyer`, l'option Veri*Factu est disponible si "
"Veri*Factu a été activé."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:146
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to generate a JSON file containing the invoice "
"details. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all corresponding documents are listed by "
"their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Envoyer` pour générer un fichier JSON contenant les "
"détails de la facture. Ce fichier est stocké comme document Veri*Factu. Dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, tous les documents correspondants sont "
"listés par leur date de création et leur statut actuel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:151
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:176
msgid ""
"To download a JSON file, click on its document in the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` "
"tab. Then, in the :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu Documents` window, click the "
"link in the :guilabel:`JSON` field."
msgstr ""
"Pour télécharger un fichier JSON, cliquer sur son document dans l'onglet "
":guilabel:`Veri*Factu`. Ensuite, dans la fenêtre :guilabel:`Ouvrir : "
"documents Veri*Factu`, cliquer sur le lien dans le champ :guilabel:`JSON`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:155
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:180
msgid ""
"The document should be sent to the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)` immediately. However, it may be delayed due to "
"mandatory waiting periods between submissions required by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. In such cases, the document "
"is automatically sent the next time a scheduled action runs."
msgstr ""
"Le document doit être envoyé immédiatement à l':abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal "
"de Administración Tributaria)`. Toutefois, il peut être retardé en raison de "
"périodes d'attente obligatoires entre les envois requises par l':abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. Dans ce cas, le document "
"est automatiquement envoyé lors de la prochaine exécution d'une action "
"planifiée."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:159
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the invoice PDF. Scan this code to "
"verify that the invoice has been received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."
msgstr ""
"Un **code QR** Veri\\*Factu apparaît sur le PDF de la facture. Scanner ce "
"code pour vérifier que la facture a été reçue et reconnue par l':abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:166
msgid "Point of sale orders"
msgstr "Commandes du point de vente"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:168
msgid ""
"Once an order has been :ref:`paid <pos/sell>`, a JSON file containing the "
"order details is generated. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:171
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` list view, select the relevant order. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all the corresponding documents are listed "
"by their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Point de Vente --> Commandes --> Commandes`. Dans la "
"vue liste :guilabel:`Commandes`, sélectionner la commande concernée. Dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Veri*Factu`, tous les documents correspondants sont "
"listés par leur date de création et leur statut actuel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:185
msgid ""
"If an invoice is generated for an order during the payment process, the "
"Veri*Factu document is :ref:`created and sent for the invoice <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Si une facture est générée pour une commande pendant le processus de "
"paiement, le document Veri*Factu est :ref:`créé et envoyé pour la facture "
"<localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` à la place."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:189
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the order receipt, even if an invoice "
"is created for the order. Scan this code to verify that the invoice has been "
"received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"
msgstr ""
"Un **code QR** Veri\\*Factu apparaît sur le ticket de commande, même si une "
"facture est créée pour la commande. Scanner ce code pour vérifier que la "
"facture a été reçue et reconnue par l':abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:194
msgid "TicketBAI"
msgstr "TicketBAI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:196
msgid ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ or "
"**TBAI** is an e-Invoicing system used by the Basque government and its "
"three provincial councils (Álava, Biscay, and Gipuzkoa)."
msgstr ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ ou "
"**TBAI** est un système de facturation électronique utilisé par le "
"gouvernement basque et ses trois conseils provinciaux (Álava, Biscaye et "
"Gipuzkoa)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:200
msgid ""
"Odoo supports the **TicketBAI (TBAI)** electronic invoicing format for all "
"three regions of the **Basque Country**. To enable **TicketBAI**, set your "
"company's :guilabel:`Country` and :guilabel:`Tax ID` "
"under :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` in "
"the :guilabel:`Companies` section."
msgstr ""
"Odoo prend en charge le format de facturation électronique **TicketBAI (TBAI)"
"** pour les trois régions du **Pays basque**. Pour activer **TicketBAI**, "
"définir le :guilabel:`Pays` et le :guilabel:`Numéro de TVA` de votre société "
"sous :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Paramètres généraux` dans la section "
":guilabel:`Sociétés`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:205
msgid ""
"Then, :ref:`install <general/install>` the module :guilabel:`Spain "
"-TicketBAI (l10n_es_edi_TBAI)`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and select a **region** in the :guilabel:`Spain "
"Localization` section's :guilabel:`Tax Agency for TBAI` field."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, :ref:`installer <general/install>` le module :guilabel:`Espagne -"
"TicketBAI (l10n_es_edi_TBAI)`, aller dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres`, et sélectionner une **région** dans le champ "
":guilabel:`Agence fiscale pour TBAI` de la section :guilabel:`Localisation "
"Espagne`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:209
msgid ""
"Once a region is selected, click :guilabel:`Manage certificates (SII/"
"TicketBAI)`, then click :guilabel:`New`, upload the certificate, and enter "
"the password provided by the tax agency."
msgstr ""
"Une fois qu'une région est sélectionnée, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Gérer les "
"certificats (SII/TicketBAI)`, puis cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`, "
"téléverser le certificat et saisir le mot de passe fourni par l'agence "
"fiscale."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:213
msgid ""
"If you are testing certificates, enable :guilabel:`Test Mode` in "
"the :guilabel:`Spain Localization` section, which can be found "
"under :guilabel:`Accounting` in the **Settings** app."
msgstr ""
"Si vous testez des certificats, activer le :guilabel:`Mode Test` dans la "
"section :guilabel:`Localisation Espagne`, qui se trouve sous "
":guilabel:`Comptabilité` dans l'application **Paramètres**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:220
msgid ""
"Once an invoice has been :doc:`created <../../finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices>` and confirmed, a TicketBAI **banner** appears at the top."
msgstr ""
"Une fois qu'une facture a été :doc:`créée <../../finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices>` et confirmée, une **bannière** TicketBAI apparaît en "
"haut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:None
msgid "TicketBAI banner at the top of the invoice once sent."
msgstr "Bannière TicketBAI en haut de la facture une fois envoyée."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:226
msgid ""
"Odoo sends invoices through TicketBAI automatically every **24 hours**. "
"However, you can click :guilabel:`Process now` to send the invoice "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Odoo envoie les factures via TicketBAI automatiquement toutes les **24 "
"heures**. Cependant, vous pouvez cliquer sur :guilabel:`Traiter maintenant` "
"pour envoyer la facture immédiatement."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:229
msgid ""
"When the invoice is **sent**, the status of the field :guilabel:`Electronic "
"Invoice` changes to :guilabel:`Sent`, and the XML file can be found in the "
"**chatter**. Under the :guilabel:`EDI Documents` tab, you can see the "
"traceability of other generated documents related to the invoice (e.g., if "
"the invoice should also be sent through the **SII**, it will appear here)."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque la facture est **envoyée**, le statut du champ :guilabel:`Facture "
"électronique` devient :guilabel:`Envoyée`, et le fichier XML se trouve dans "
"le **chatter**. Sous l'onglet :guilabel:`Documents EDI`, vous pouvez voir la "
"traçabilité des autres documents générés liés à la facture (par exemple, si "
"la facture doit également être envoyée via le **SII**, elle apparaîtra ici)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:235
